{"tid":1583391,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"PT唔做比人叫毀約應該點?","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T07:17:35.000Z","uid":269038,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1674f94055b8d3cb3850a427615aac8a18d67bb9","tid":1583391,"uid":269038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"Part-time番左2個半星期, 覺得人工又低環境又差.<br />\n每星期12個鐘倒 (時多時少),<br />\n但事情係我簽左份合約, 話要3個月前通知唔做.<br />\n好啦我通知佢3個月後唔做,<br />\n之後再同佢講我唔得閒, 要每星期番少一日.<br />\n佢即刻打尼話我「同毀約冇分別」, 又擺d細路上台 (PT兒童手工班) 話成日轉老師對小朋友唔好.<br />\n<br />\n心諗咩叫「同毀約冇分別」???? 佢搞到我連剩低嗰3個月都唔想做.<br />\n我番唔夠4星期18個鐘 per wk, 毀約應該冇野啦. 但係如果份約話3個月前要通知佢, 我唔夠3個月就毀約又會點?<br />\n<br />\n另外如果我就咁每星期番少日, 佢真係會當我毀約? 真係咁On 9???"},{"pid":"aeec6d6cc57a90fc97664536b5f403a01d687589","tid":1583391,"uid":269681,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:41:36.000Z","msg":"我地連你份約講咩都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa558a6a8206190966d45cb29d4ba8555731a06","tid":1583391,"uid":8313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"你張約點寫先"},{"pid":"1dfbe8b5d2a66572da2bf8db7b54b613bca60433","tid":1583391,"uid":183194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"合約精神<br />\n<br />\n唔好似支那咁，中英聯合聲名簽左都唔認"},{"pid":"b17cbf2439f5e79f4e6d8e4fa2aa596b71e9eb2d","tid":1583391,"uid":32753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"簽約前要諗清楚"},{"pid":"0750a892dbb800a16febddca44901ad2ddf64040","tid":1583391,"uid":259579,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"3個月通知期你都簽咁係你問題啦"},{"pid":"a9e9aa36648b6a44cca088794135e7a47862e365","tid":1583391,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊 - 會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人 - 食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG136wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=ec6a64b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"429160100d042d5ac3a95e90471f0a909cc10318","tid":1583391,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"咩公司3個月通知，正常1個月通知，仲要係兼職?"},{"pid":"8463a4d66fd249c87d509911905c5b76102f3318","tid":1583391,"uid":7332,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:48:51.000Z","msg":"Labour law 可以淩駕不合理合約<br />\nSend email quote labour law同佢傾<br />\n所有對話錄音"},{"pid":"1899e665d1b452e03a4d0a0b30da6a988671cd9d","tid":1583391,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"3個月???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6484247fe4859e96fe2bb3970f88a8e2baed92","tid":1583391,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"三個月通知都唔荒係咩好嘢啦 咁都簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43101c0961f405fa5a6013b79ea18d7bfef6ff26","tid":1583391,"uid":269038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429160100d042d5ac3a95e90471f0a909cc10318","tid":1583391,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"咩公司3個月通知，正常1個月通知，仲要係兼職?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"3個月通知我都照通知啦.